        </item>
        <item>
            <title>港铁 45 周年推出《穿越铁路秘景》系列，第一集探访九龙湾维修车厂</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/05/mtr-45th/life-tech/smartcity/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mtr-45th</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/05/mtr-45th/life-tech/smartcity/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 09:30:46 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[九龙湾车厂]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[港铁]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[港铁 45 周年]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1273264</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">为庆祝与香港连系相伴四十五载，港铁公司发布《穿越铁路秘景》系列第一集，带大家探访位于九龙湾的元祖级维修车厂，并深入通车时的第一代车厂控制室，一窥港铁日常营运背后的舞台，分享铁路鲜为人知的点滴。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_49813"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/n77WZUSARhA?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p style="text-align: center;">▲《穿越铁路秘景》系列第一集</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>第一代车厂控制室：重回「冰封」逾 </strong><strong>20 </strong><strong>年的时空</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">影片中，揭开序幕的是屹立在九龙湾车厂北面的塔形建筑物。塔部顶层正是港铁第一代车厂控制室，是昔日主管车务控制的人员鸟瞰及掌管列车调度及进出车厂的核心地方。为配合车厂系统数码化及以全面营运模式运作，控制室于二零零三停止运作。而控制塔的环境与设备至今依然保存著昔日初建的风貌。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273265 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241105at-3-694x387.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="387" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241105at-3-694x387.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241105at-3-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273266 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2-435x580.jpeg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2-435x580.jpeg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2.jpeg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273267 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241105at-4-694x458.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="458" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241105at-4-694x458.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241105at-4.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲九龙湾车厂北面的塔形建筑物，塔部顶层是港铁第一代车厂控制室</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273268 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/3-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/3-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/3-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273269 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/4-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/4-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/4-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲为配合车厂系统数码化及以全面营运模式运作，控制室于二零零三停止运作</p><h2></h2><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>九龙湾车厂：元祖级车厂，市区线列车之维修心脏</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">自一九七九年投入服务的九龙湾车厂是港铁首个车厂，亦是市区线列车维修的心脏地带，它见证了港铁从单一路线发展到今天完善的铁路网络，同时是现存最多款式的市区线列车会汇集作日常「体检」的车厂。45 年来，九龙湾车厂亦培育了众多的列车维修医生，全年无休地为列车进行检查和维修，他们对每部列车中超过 10,000 件的零件都了如指掌。随著镜头深入车厂内部，大家可以看到车厂的各项设施，包括列车停泊路段、维修设备等，凸显车厂在确保列车安全运行中的关键作用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273270 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/5-694x389.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/5-694x389.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/5.jpg 1093w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273271 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241105at-5-694x388.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241105at-5-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241105at-5-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲九龙湾车厂是港铁首个车厂</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273272 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241105at-6-694x458.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="458" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241105at-6-694x458.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241105at-6.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲九龙湾车厂亦培育了众多的列车维修医生，全年无休地为列车进行检查和维修</p><h2></h2><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>拍摄背后：严谨规划并出动无人机</strong><strong>拍摄</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">作为元祖级的维修重地，九龙湾车厂肩负列车日常检查和维修的使命，年终无休地运作。为了让大家能够窥探香港高效率列车服务背后的工作，制作团队使用了无人机拍摄。拍摄前进行了全方位场地勘察、规划飞行路线。在刚过去的周末，港铁亦邀请了铁路爱好者、影像创作工作者及文化艺术的内容营运编辑等组成「港铁隐藏秘景探索队」，在退休车厂主任和现役工程师的带领下踏足平日禁区，深入了解港铁四十五年来的发展历程，并以更多不同角度将相关场景与故事分享予公众。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273273 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241105at-7-694x389.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241105at-7-694x389.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241105at-7-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273275 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241105at-8-694x455.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="455" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241105at-8-694x455.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241105at-8.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲制作团队使用了无人机拍摄</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>与众同贺港铁 </strong><strong>45 </strong><strong>周年活动</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">除了「港铁探索隐藏秘景」系列企划外，港铁早前更推出了一系列精彩活动，包括『绿铁 B「动」乐日』、红磡站的「站见」铁路展、「港铁 45 周年主题列车」及首个户外大型铁路主题嘉年华「Chill Fun 铁路乐园」。承接以上港铁 45 周年活动，再配合「港铁探索隐藏秘景」系列企划，不只是对港铁历史的致敬，更是展望未来的重要一步。《穿越铁路秘景》系列一连两集，第二集有同样精彩的内容，且看下回分解。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273276 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/10-387x580.png" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/10-387x580.png 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/10.png 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲「港铁探索隐藏秘景」系列企划</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/11/05/mtr-45th/life-tech/smartcity/">港铁 45 周年推出《穿越铁路秘景》系列，第一集探访九龙湾维修车厂</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/05/mtr-45th/life-tech/smartcity/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
